<p>Materials are open without restrictions.</p>  </accessrestrict>
  <acqinfo id="aspace_05288cdad03773cee95594c387e68770">
    <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
<p>Materials were donated by David Eliscu in 2001. The accessio numbers associated with these gifts are 2001.045, 2001.149, and NPA.2002.049.</p>  </acqinfo>
  <arrangement id="aspace_5a792cbbe75e21b4b4db109a69389dc8">
